# How to Set Up Niama AI (Local Version)

## Requirements
- Python 3.10+
- Node.js
- Git
- Internet

## Steps
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Modu2018/Niama-ai-website.git

cd Niama-ai-website

cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt

python app.py


